---
layout: "base.njk"
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container flow">
    <div class="hero__content flow">
      <h1 class="section-title">Welcome to InsightFief!</h1>
      <p>
        Halo dan selamat datang di InsightFief! Di sini, kami menjelajahi keajaiban sains, topik menarik, dan sejarah yang memukau. Baik Anda penggemar sains, pecinta sejarah, atau sekadar penasaran, Anda berada di tempat yang tepat.
      </p>
      <div class="flex-group">
        <a href="#featured-articles" class="btn btn--primary"
          >Featured articles</a
        >
        <a href="./blog" class="btn btn--neutral">Most recent articles</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="//unsplash.it/510" alt="" class="hero__image" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="featured-articles" class="featured-articles">
  <div class="container flow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Featured articles</h2>
    <p class="text-center">
      Welcome to InsightFief! Let's explore together.
    </p>
    <ul role="list" class="articles__list flow">
    {%- for post in collections.featured | reverse -%}
      {% include 'article-snippet.njk' %}
    {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
